
ROOM ROOMS ROOMFLAG
 
   DARK           1
   DEATH          2
   NO_MOB         4
   INDOORS        8
   PEACEFUL      16    No fighting  (please also set NO_HEAL with this flag)
   NOSTEAL       32    No Thieving  */ Does not work (yet)
   NO_SUM        64    No summoning of creatures in these rooms */
   NO_MAGIC     128 
   TUNNEL       256    only X people in room (X set by edit tunn) */
   PRIVATE      512    No teleport to here, no goto when more than 2 people
   SILENCE     1024    The only form of communication is wiznet and signing
   NO_ORDER    2048    charmed mobs will not accept master's orders here
   ANARCHY     4096    pc's may kill pc's here.  Can't summon a pc into here.
   HAVE_TO_WALK 8192   no astral, portal or teleport into this room
   ARENA      16384    /* not yet implemented completely */
   NO-HEAL    32768    no regeneration of mana/hits here. 
   undefined  65536    doubles regen rate for owner of house
